videos.description: The Warriors' Juan Toscano-Anderson comes up with the steal and races down the court to throw down an uncontested windmill dunk on the break.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Toscano-Anderson throws down sick windmill on the break) 2021/03/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Toscano-Anderson throws down sick windmill on the break

videos.description: Kyle Guy throws a bounce pass inside to Chimezie Metu who goes up to deliver a powerful slam at the rim for the Kings.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Guy finds Metu for powerful dunk) 2021/03/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Guy finds Metu for powerful dunk

videos.description: Tyrese Haliburton puts the moves on his defender to make him stumble, then pulls up to drain a step-back 3-pointer and draw the foul.
videos.headline: Haliburton cashes out and-1 3-pointer

videos.description: De'Aaron Fox slithers through the Warriors' defense and uses a step-back move to get free and knock down a smooth mid-range shot.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Fox slices up Warriors' defense for smooth step-back shot) 2021/03/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fox slices up Warriors' defense for smooth step-back shot
